    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-10-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-10-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="175"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d175">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d175fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché, Moscow,
                        via the White House Map Room and Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hyde Park</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-10-30">30 October
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Personal and secret for the Secretary of State only from the President. My
                        302232.<note n="2" xml:id="d175fn2">Telegram of October 30, 1943, <hi
                            rend="italic">supra.</hi>
                    </note>
                </p>
                <p>Final disposition of all Italian ships should apply to those used by British and
                    Americans as well as to those used by Russians.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
